{"tid":1025792,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾車果陣臭味到底係咩味?","createTime":"2019-02-17T15:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T07:22:17.000Z","uid":4052,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7e7175cee535f9a2dca7a8897ee5ccf8b1df3ac2","tid":1025792,"uid":4052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"明明架架垃圾車裝既垃圾都唔一樣，但係部部垃圾車都係果陣臭味，到底果陣臭味點嚟既呢？"},{"pid":"4c764ba1b5041dd8af43a290f1a6f2cd0b6e5f1b","tid":1025792,"uid":207005,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:06:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾味"},{"pid":"9d04a096f566df8fcc2c4a40ea24ea89a163e467","tid":1025792,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:08:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10591f13d7de65c44da8402a8d3054b1d0b91604","tid":1025792,"uid":20117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:09:32.000Z","msg":"細菌分解垃圾既味(好似係)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f097602cf736b054b0ebbb18896a76656de388","tid":1025792,"uid":30578,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:45:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾的厭氧發酵過程中會產生大量的填埋氣，其組分通常為：50%~70%左右的甲烷，30%~50%左右的二氧化碳，以及1%左右的微量組分。而惡臭，就是由這1%的微量組分中的某些物質引起的。這些微量組分包括有機化合物和無機化合物，種類繁多而濃度極低，填埋場能夠檢出的物質可達一百多種，濃度在ppm或ppb級。可以把這些物質分為幾類：含硫化合物（硫化氫、硫醇、硫醚等）、含氧化合物（醇、醛、酮、酯等）、烷烴、烯烴、鹵代烴、萜烯以及芳香烴，對了還有氨氣。其中，硫化物以及含氧化合物由於嗅閾值較低而濃度相對較高（因為是厭氧、兼氧發酵初期主要產物），往往會導致嚴重的惡臭。"},{"pid":"b7e3d5955ec3b08211b46235b5f99991e9325250","tid":1025792,"uid":192409,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"輸6球嗰陣"},{"pid":"ea365319672349756486a02a2156ad68b2cd1f29","tid":1025792,"uid":20290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"食物腐壞嘅味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0cd13dc210634697ac9d8dd3d4d197700b4356","tid":1025792,"uid":232754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:40:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得係係變壞嘅生果"},{"pid":"224f8a9b7f2b18d8f4eceb87040730f14e7c747b","tid":1025792,"uid":74168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7e3d5955ec3b08211b46235b5f99991e9325250","tid":1025792,"uid":192409,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"輸6球嗰陣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}